Tie/PureDB version 0.02
=======================

Tie::PureDB - Perl extension for pure-db

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires pure-db-2.1
which is included in this archive..

